Out !

189
00:19:12,450 --> 00:19:13,550
Good job !

190
00:19:13,550 --> 00:19:14,250
All right !

191
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:18,100
He was short...

192
00:19:18,100 --> 00:19:21,350
Until the second year of junior high, I was a snot-nosed midget.

193
00:19:22,650 --> 00:19:28,650
Finally, my height caught up, and I started to think about maybe looking for a girlfriend...

194
00:19:28,650 --> 00:19:31,150
...but all the girls that interested me were in the midst of their first love.

195
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:43,290
What is it ?

196
00:19:44,300 --> 00:19:47,240
Um, well, nothing.

197
00:19:56,120 --> 00:19:57,340
All right ! Go !

198
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:05,700
Out !

199
00:20:09,090 --> 00:20:12,500
Do you really want 
to disband this team ?

200
00:20:13,030 --> 00:20:15,500
I made this promise
to make that happen.

201
00:20:33,140 --> 00:20:35,120
It's hot.

202
00:20:35,120 --> 00:20:36,390
It's summer.

203
00:20:42,980 --> 00:20:44,810
Strike ! Batter out !

204
00:20:49,100 --> 00:20:52,190
All right ! 
All that's left is the ninth inning !

205
00:20:52,190 --> 00:20:54,100
Now, it's getting interesting, Koga !

206
